The Loan  Agreement is made and entered at the place and on the date as mentioned in Schedule A (herein referred to as “Schedule A”) between: 

Borrower(s) (Which expression shall unless repugnant to the context or meaning thereof be deemed to include his/her heirs, legal representatives, successors, executors and assigns etc. more particularly described and set out in Schedule A (herein referred to as “Borrower(s)”) of the one part;

							AND 

CreditAccess Grameen Limited(CA Grameen), a Company incorporated under the provisions of the Companies Act, 1956 and registered with the Reserve Bank of India as a Non-Banking Financial Company -Micro Finance Institution (NBFC-MFI) having its Registered Office situated at #49 (Old no. # 725), 46th Cross, 8th Block, Jayanagar, Bangalore- 560070 hereinafter referred to as the “Company” which term shall deemed to mean and include unless the context otherwise requires or permits, its successors  and permitted assigns of the Other Part;

The Borrower(s) and the Company shall together be referred to as ‘Parties’ and individually as ‘Party’.

