20. Any notice required or permitted by this Agreement shall be in writing and shall be delivered as follows, with notice deemed to be given as indicated:

(a) If by personal delivery, when delivered personally and acknowledgment taken;

(b) If by courier, upon written verification of receipt;

(c) If by telefax or facsimile transmission, upon acknowledgment of receipt of electronic transmission; or

(d) If by certified or registered post with acknowledgement due, return of acknowledgement receipt. Notice shall be sent to the addresses set forth above and if any party changes the above-mentioned address, then the same shall be communicated to the other party in writing immediately.
